{{TennisEventInfo|2011|Morocco Tennis Tour – Meknes| | date=February 14 – February 19 | edition=4th | location=[[Meknes]], [[Morocco]] | champs={{flagicon|CZE}} [[Jaroslav Pospíšil]] | champd={{flagicon|PHI}} [[Treat Conrad Huey]] / {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Simone Vagnozzi]] }}
The '''2011 [[Morocco Tennis Tour – Meknes]]''' was a professional [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Clay courts|outdoor clay courts]]. It was part of the [[2011 ATP Challenger Tour]]. It took place in [[Meknes]], [[Morocco]] between 14 and 19 February 2011.
