'''Estadio Chochi Sosa''' (Chochi sosa Stadium) is a concert and sports venue located in [[Tegucigalpa]], [[Honduras]]. It was completed in 1989 and is part of the [[Tegucigalpa Olympic Village]].<ref>https://es.foursquare.com/v/estadio-chochi-sosa/4cd202383e63721ec11ba7cc</ref>
