The '''Grand Prix of Sochi''' is a [[road bicycle racing|road cycling]] [[stage race (cycling)|stage race]] held annually in [[Sochi]], [[Russia]]. It was first run in 2005 and is part of the [[UCI Europe Tour]] as a [[2.2]] category race. No rider has had more than one victory.

