'''Roberts Center''' was a 4,400-seat multi-purpose [[arena]] in [[Chestnut Hill, Massachusetts]].  It opened in 1958.  It was home to the [[Boston College]] Eagles [[basketball]] teams until the [[Conte Forum]] opened in 1988.<ref>http://newspapers.bc.edu/cgi-bin/bostonsh?a=d&d=bcheights19880201.2.45</ref>

