{{unreferenced|date=May 2016}}
'''Stade Marchand''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Brazzaville]], [[Republic of the Congo]].  It is used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home of [[Diables Noirs]] of the [[Congo Premier League]]. It has a capacity of 5,000 people.

